When you add them all together you obtain a total of about 9,730.78. (A quick “sanity check” shows that roughly 29 entries averaging roughly 335 yield a total in the low‐ to mid‑9000’s.)

Because no “Interest Receivables” entry is recorded on the opening day (2023‑12‑31) the initial balance is zero.

Thus the balance‐sheet values for the interest receivable item are:

 • Interest Receivable Initial Value = 0.00  
 • Interest Receivable End Value = 9730.78
